textAfterTable: 49 Songs Customer Reviews Great Music For Any Ceremony           by sam sam military man Whether you are looking for music to remember the fond moments of your military career or looking for something to play at a loved ones memorial service this album is for you. Performed by the US Air Force band a group that has been a part of american history since the 1940's this album has all the important ceremonial music that you could need. The performances are excellent and each track will give the full feeling of reverence and valor that our members of the armed force truly deserve. If you like this one you should also check out:Music For Honors and Ceremonies Both will be great for your collection and just what you need for that special personal ceremony of your own.
